Author: dexydex
Text: I’m definitely returning it! I took a picture & then put the piece of glass back in with the other slice of cake. I should’ve went with my gut feeling of it being odd that they had just the one container of slices for sale because I have never seen them sell that cake in the individual servings, only as a whole cake. I’m sad though because it’s one of my favorite cakes from there!

Author: BabyBaphomet_
Text: Id freak tf out!!! See if you can return it. That's messed up.
